| C1   | C2   | C3   |
+------+------+------+
|    5 |    6 |    7 |
|    7 |    5 |    9 |
|    9 |    4 |   11 |
|   12 |   12 |    3 |
|    2 |    3 |    4 |
|    4 |    5 |    6 |
|    5 |    6 |    7 |
|    9 |    3 |   11 |
+------+------+------+

